<p>Julian Cole, Liane Siebenhaar, and rOobin Golestan have put together an awesome little talk series called <a href="http://theplanningsalon.com/" target="_blank">The Planning Salon</a> and I sat in on the above G+ Hangout interview this morning. </p>
