<h1 class="entry-title"><a href="http://whatconsumesme.com/2013/posts-ive-written/the-google-reader-pocalypse-is-coming/" rel="bookmark" title="Permanent Link to the google reader-pocalypse is coming" style="color:#EF3061;">the google reader-pocalypse is coming</a></h1>
<p><p><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-11472" title="google reader shut down july 1st" src="http://whatconsumesme.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/05/deadreader.png" alt="" width="610" height="254"/></p>
